Title: About The Enhancon Mechanism
Authors: P. Merlatti
Comments: To appear in the proceedings of the RTN meeting ``The Quantum
  Structure of Spacetime and the Geometric Nature of Fundamental
  Interactions'', (Corfu`, September 2001)
Journal-ref: Fortsch.Phys. 50 (2002) 936-941
\\
  I study the enhancon mechanism for fractional D-branes in conifold and
orbifold backgrounds and show how it can resolve the ``repulson'' singularity
of these geometries. In particular I show that the consistency of the excision
process requires that the interior space be not empty.
